                                    </div>
                                    <h3 class="card-title">Prompt Library</h3>
                                    <p>Access a vast collection of expertly crafted prompts for any task or creative endeavor.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg">
                                <div class="card-body items-center text-center">
                                    <div class="p-4 bg-secondary/10 rounded-full mb-4">
                                        <i data-lucide="git-merge" class="w-8 h-8 text-secondary"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <h3 class="card-title">Automated Workflows</h3>
                                    <p>Streamline complex processes with pre-built workflows that you can import and use instantly.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg">
                                <div class="card-body items-center text-center">
                                    <div class="p-4 bg-accent/10 rounded-full mb-4">
                                        <i data-lucide="wrench" class="w-8 h-8 text-accent"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <h3 class="card-title">Curated Tools</h3>
